title: Jake Owen || Surviving Barstool on A Snow Day
description:
Subscribe, Rate, and Leave a Review! -NYC has it's first blizzard in years -Steve Cohen quit twitter and Nate went over the top at him -Surviving Barstool is heating up -Top 5 Reality show villains of all time -Voicemails Jake Owen returns to the show to talk about his role in the new movie "Our Friend". We talk about his relationship with the Fore Play guys, his recent engagement, and how he's currently working on a rap song! To cap it all off, Jake generously donates $100k to the Barstool Fund. All around awesome guy and we're happy to have him back on.
